entries.journal_entry_description: Turning the tables on the terrorists, the time has come to infiltrate the Mummer bunker.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Initiate the assault on the Mummer Bunker by attacking their main forces there. Defeat Mummer toxers, Mummer banes, and Mummer salvers.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Bad news. There are bio-chemical bombs in the Mummer base. Neutralize them.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find the bio-chemical bombs in the Mummer bunker and neutralize them.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Good job eliminating the threat posed by those bio-chemical bombs. Now to finish this. Go after the Mummer leaders.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Mummer Chief Scientist, Crimsol Vaighn.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Mummer base commander, Jaye Hawkson.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Return to Sergeant Brunser and let her know of your success against the Mummers.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to Pooja Naberrie and let her know you've completed your assignment involving the terrorists.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Battle your way into the Mummer base by fighting Mummer Salvers.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Assault the Mummer base and defeat some Mummer banes.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Attack on the Mummer base by taking down some Mummer toxers.
